702651f-a.text:
Twenty Third Ave., east side, between Cropsey and Warehouse Aves. A view of the Brooklyn Yacht Club, still in existence in 1908.
About 1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

702652f.text:
Twenty Third Ave., west side, between Cropsey and Warehouse Aves., showing the Royal Arcanum Yacht Club, and the Brooklyn Yacht Club at the
left and right respectively.
About 1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
